	(gr_text "TestSteps:\n1. Make sure TP_H1 = 10 V, TP_L1 = -10 V to get start.\n2. Use50Ohm on J8, manual setpoint. See TP4=5*Setpoint\n3. Put jumper on J12 to make a pure P, Gain = 1.5, verify at TP5\n4. Move that jumper to J4 to change it to pure integrator, verify it locks itself.\n5. Verify voltage limiter works; Remove R5 and put Bourns on J1 etc... "
